|    1 | SIMPLE        | products | NULL         | ALL    | NULL            | NULL  | NULL      | NULL  |   9836 |       1.11 | Using where; Using temporary; Using filesort |
+------+---------------+----------+--------------+--------+-----------------+-------+-----------+-------+--------+------------+----------------------------------------------+

