|    1 | SIMPLE        | u       | NULL         | eq_ref | PRIMARY         | PRIMARY | 8         | test_index.o.user_id |      1 |        100 | NULL           |
+------+---------------+---------+--------------+--------+-----------------+---------+-----------+----------------------+--------+------------+----------------+

## Column Selectivity:
{"orders":{"amount":94.296%,"order_id":100%,"ship_city":0.01%,"ship_country":0.01%},"users":{"user_id":100%,"username":100%}}

## Original SQL:
SELECT 
    o.order_id, 
    o.amount, 
    o.ship_country, 
    o.ship_city, 
    u.user_id, 
    u.username
FROM 
    orders o
LEFT JOIN 
    users u ON o.user_id = u.user_id
ORDER BY 
    o.order_id ASC, 
    o.ship_city ASC;

