## Column Selectivity:
{"users":{"user_id":100%,"username":100%},"access_logs":{"user_id":5.0460%,"created_at":1.3960%},}

## Original SQL:
SELECT 
    u.user_id, 
    u.username, 
    (SELECT MAX(created_at) 
     FROM access_logs 
     WHERE user_id = u.user_id) AS last_login_time
FROM 
    users u
WHERE 
    u.vip_level > 0;

